  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The House</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starting as a curious journalist, you'll find yourself immersed in paranormal activity, horror and psychological suspense as you try to escape from an abandoned house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore, find, decrypt and get out of here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Atmosphere</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmosphere is crucial in defining the soul of a game, and it is incredibly important to me. While developing \"The House,\" I paid attention to every detail. The dark and mysterious atmosphere of the game is designed to draw players in and make every moment more thrilling. This way, you can fully experience the tension and horror the game offers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624100/extras/c3f64bd489f13233c409a22dde542447.poster.avif?t=1739206878\" width=602 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624100/extras/c3f64bd489f13233c409a22dde542447.webm?t=1739206878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624100/extras/c3f64bd489f13233c409a22dde542447.mp4?t=1739206878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Equipment</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game contains content that may not be suitable for all age groups. The game includes frequent blood and profanity. Additionally, there are elements that may be disturbing for individuals with panic attacks and epilepsy, as well as mild nudity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624100/extras/5aaa6ab2c20456427292fe8977ccb448.poster.avif?t=1739206878\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624100/extras/5aaa6ab2c20456427292fe8977ccb448.webm?t=1739206878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624100/extras/5aaa6ab2c20456427292fe8977ccb448.mp4?t=1739206878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully examine notes and photographs you find.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your equipment carefully, such as cameras, night vision and flashlights.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch the tapes you find, put together the passwords and open the secret rooms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to take keys, batteries and any equipment you can use.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The House</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starting as a curious journalist, you'll find yourself immersed in paranormal activity, horror and psychological suspense as you try to escape from an abandoned house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore, find, decrypt and get out of here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Atmosphere</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmosphere is crucial in defining the soul of a game, and it is incredibly important to me. While developing \"The House,\" I paid attention to every detail. The dark and mysterious atmosphere of the game is designed to draw players in and make every moment more thrilling. This way, you can fully experience the tension and horror the game offers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624100/extras/c3f64bd489f13233c409a22dde542447.poster.avif?t=1739206878\" width=602 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624100/extras/c3f64bd489f13233c409a22dde542447.webm?t=1739206878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624100/extras/c3f64bd489f13233c409a22dde542447.mp4?t=1739206878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Equipment</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game contains content that may not be suitable for all age groups. The game includes frequent blood and profanity. Additionally, there are elements that may be disturbing for individuals with panic attacks and epilepsy, as well as mild nudity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624100/extras/5aaa6ab2c20456427292fe8977ccb448.poster.avif?t=1739206878\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624100/extras/5aaa6ab2c20456427292fe8977ccb448.webm?t=1739206878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624100/extras/5aaa6ab2c20456427292fe8977ccb448.mp4?t=1739206878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully examine notes and photographs you find.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your equipment carefully, such as cameras, night vision and flashlights.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch the tapes you find, put together the passwords and open the secret rooms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to take keys, batteries and any equipment you can use.</p></li></ul>",
